This error occurs because the function returned by the `useChangeCopiedStateToDefaultAfter` hook returns two elements: a boolean (`copied`) and a function to set the boolean (`setCopied`). In the `onClick` function, you are passing only the boolean to `setCopied` function. 

To fix this error, you need to pass the function returned by the `useChangeCopiedStateToDefaultAfter` hook to the `onClick` event and then call it with the value `true` to update the `copied` state.

